{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium Shopify Reel Video Section using Shopify Liquid, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This section must be fully compatible with Shopify Theme Customizer and support Shopify-hosted videos uploaded directly from the Shopify admin/customizer.
    
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Videos will ONLY come from Shopify video picker/upload.
    * Do NOT use external video URLs.
    * Use Shopify native video settings and Liquid schema blocks.
    * Section must be production-ready, responsive, smooth, and optimized.
    
    SECTION STRUCTURE:
    
    * Create a horizontal reel carousel section inspired by premium D2C brands like SuperYou and MaxProtein.
    * Use a modern cinematic layout with luxury UI/UX.
    * Section should feel immersive, smooth, and premium.
    
    SHOPIFY CUSTOMIZER SETTINGS:
    Provide controls inside Shopify schema for:
    
    * Section background color picker
    * Background overlay opacity slider
    * Section top padding
    * Section bottom padding
    * Reel gap spacing
    * Border radius control
    * Hover scale intensity
    * Navigation button color
    * Navigation button background
    * Navigation icon color
    * Fullscreen overlay opacity
    * Auto-scroll speed
    * Enable/disable autoplay
    * Enable/disable auto-scroll
    
    VIDEO BLOCK SETTINGS:
    Create exactly 15 blocks maximum.
    Each block should support:
    
    * Shopify video upload picker
    * Poster image
    * Optional reel title
    * Optional reel link
    * Enable/disable individual reel
    
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Empty blocks must NOT render.
    * Only uploaded videos should appear.
    * Dynamic rendering required.
    
    DESKTOP LAYOUT:
    
    * Show exactly 4 videos visible.
    * Horizontal reel layout.
    * Equal spacing between reels.
    * Premium modern spacing and padding.
    * Videos should NEVER get cut when hover scaling.
    * Add outer container padding to prevent clipping.
    * Smooth snapping behavior.
    * Mouse drag support.
    * Mouse wheel horizontal scroll support.
    * Working navigation arrows on both sides.
    
    MOBILE LAYOUT:
    
    * Show 3 partial videos visible.
    * Smooth touch swipe support.
    * Momentum scrolling.
    * Snap scrolling.
    * Optimized spacing and sizing for mobile.
    * Touch drag must work smoothly.
    
    VIDEO CARD EFFECTS:
    
    * Rounded corners.
    * Premium shadows.
    * Slight hover enlarge effect.
    * Hover scale should smoothly increase size slightly.
    * IMPORTANT:
      Hover scaling must NOT crop or cut video from edges.
    * Add overflow visible where needed.
    * Use transform scale instead of resizing dimensions.
    * Smooth transition easing.
    
    VIDEO BEHAVIOR:
    
    * Videos autoplay muted.
    * Loop continuously.
    * No controls in normal carousel mode.
    * Videos pause when outside viewport.
    * Videos lazy load for performance.
    * Use Intersection Observer.
    * Autoplay should work properly on mobile.
    
    AUTO SCROLL:
    
    * Smooth infinite horizontal auto-scroll.
    * Pause auto-scroll on:
    
      * hover
      * touch
      * dragging
      * fullscreen open
    * Resume after inactivity.
    * Smooth cinematic speed.
    
    NAVIGATION BUTTONS:
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Navigation buttons MUST fully work.
    * Left/right buttons should scroll properly.
    * Add smooth animated transitions.
    * Buttons should remain clickable above videos.
    * Add proper z-index handling.
    * Buttons should work on both desktop and mobile.
    * Use glassmorphism style buttons.
    
    DRAG FUNCTIONALITY:
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Drag/swipe MUST work smoothly.
    * Fix dragging behavior completely.
    * Mouse drag on desktop.
    * Touch swipe on mobile.
    * Prevent accidental text/image selection while dragging.
    * Add grabbing cursor while dragging.
    * Use momentum/inertia feel.
    * Prevent jitter or lag.
    * Maintain smooth 60fps performance.
    
    FULLSCREEN MODAL:
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Fullscreen mode must ONLY show the video.
    * Header, announcement bar, and page content must NOT appear.
    * Fullscreen overlay must cover the ENTIRE viewport.
    * Use:
    
      * position: fixed
      * inset: 0
      * width: 100vw
      * height: 100vh
      * very high z-index
    * Disable body scrolling when modal opens.
    
    FULLSCREEN UI:
    When user clicks a reel:
    
    * Open fullscreen reel modal.
    * Black overlay background.
    * Add opacity control from Shopify settings.
    * Show ONLY the video centered.
    * Hide website header completely.
    * Hide all page UI behind modal.
    
    FULLSCREEN VIDEO CONTROLS:
    IMPORTANT:
    Enable ALL controls in fullscreen:
    
    * Play/pause
    * Sound mute/unmute
    * Volume control
    * Progress bar
    * Fullscreen native control
    * Next reel button
    * Previous reel button
    * Close button
    * Keyboard navigation
    * Touch swipe navigation
    
    IMPORTANT:
    
    * Sound toggle MUST work.
    * Navigation controls MUST appear.
    * Previous/next buttons MUST work.
    * Controls should auto-hide after inactivity.
    * Reappear on mouse movement/touch.
    
    FULLSCREEN NAVIGATION:
    
    * Left/right arrows for next previous reel.
    * Keyboard support:
    
      * ESC closes modal
      * Left arrow previous reel
      * Right arrow next reel
    * Mobile swipe support in fullscreen.
    * Disable carousel auto-scroll during fullscreen.
    
    PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATION:
    
    * Lazy load videos.
    * GPU accelerated transforms.
    * Use translate3d transforms.
    * Avoid layout shifts.
    * Smooth animations only.
    * Optimized for Shopify storefront speed.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-reel-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-reel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .ai-reel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .ai-reel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.reel_gap }}px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    overflow-y: visible;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    cursor: grab;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .ai-reel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-reel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}.dragging {
    cursor: grabbing;
    scroll-behavior: auto;
  }

  .ai-reel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - (3 * {{ block.settings.reel_gap }}px)) / 4);
    min-width: calc((100% - (3 * {{ block.settings.reel_gap }}px)) / 4);
    position: relative;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .ai-reel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: scale({{ block.settings.hover_scale }});
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-reel-video-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-reel-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-reel-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.overlay_opacity }}));
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-reel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-reel-nav-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: {{ block.settings.nav_btn_bg }};
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: {{ block.settings.nav_icon_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 10;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ai-reel-nav-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-reel-nav-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}.prev {
    left: 0;
  }

  .ai-reel-nav-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}.next {
    right: 0;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.fullscreen_overlay_opacity }});
    z-index: 99999;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: flex;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-close-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 100;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-close-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 100;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}.prev {
    left: 20px;
  }

  .ai-reel-fullscreen-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}.next {
    right: 20px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-reel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-reel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - (2 * {{ block.settings.reel_gap }}px)) / 3);
      min-width: calc((100% - (2 * {{ block.settings.reel_gap }}px)) / 3);
    }

    .ai-reel-nav-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
    }

    .ai-reel-fullscreen-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .ai-reel-fullscreen-video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      border-radius: 0;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<reel-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}
